"""
main.py — The Orchestrator (V7 Flawless Precision).

Entry point for the Supervisor AI. V7 builds on V6 Unbreakable with
3 precision fixes. 9 core systems + 3 V7 patches:

  1. LOCKFILE MEMORY (Anti-Amnesia): .supervisor_lock prevents duplicate
     prompt injection after crash-reboots.

  2. AUTO-RECONNECT ENGINE: Catches TargetClosedError from Playwright
     when IDE webviews refresh, re-fetches the page, and continues.

  3. APPROVAL SNIPER: Lightning-fast DOM check for "Always run" /
     "Run Alt+Enter" buttons BEFORE expensive Vision calls.

  4. ERADICATE page.wait_for_timeout: ZERO instances. All waits use
     asyncio.sleep() which cannot crash when the page navigates.

  5. NAVIGATION DEFENSE: Detects if AI hijacked the main IDE window
     to localhost, forces go_back(), and injects a reprimand.

  6. 180-SECOND BRAIN: Every Gemini CLI timeout is 180s globally.
     No 30s/60s surprises anywhere.

  7. MANDATE FIREWALL: SUPERVISOR_MANDATE.md explicitly forbids
     window hijacking with the exact anti-hijack rule.

  8. BULLETPROOF WORKSPACE LOCKING: --new-window flag prevents
     old workspace contamination.

  9. DYNAMIC PAGE RESOLUTION: _get_best_page() always finds the
     freshest valid IDE page after reconnects.
"""

